391
00:17:00,480 --> 00:17:02,140
Saya telah mengatakan apa yang perlu saya katakan.

392
00:17:05,440 --> 00:17:06,240
akan datang?

393
00:17:16,720 --> 00:17:17,589
Mengikut

394
00:17:17,589 --> 00:17:18,720
kepada data daripada

395
00:17:18,720 --> 00:17:20,240
kami Jabatan Pengurusan Perniagaan,

396
00:17:20,240 --> 00:17:22,109
pendapatan restoran Cina
telah mencapai tahap tinggi baru

397
00:17:22,109 --> 00:17:23,970
dalam minggu pertama sejak dibuka.

398
00:17:24,589 --> 00:17:27,790
Kadar penghunian bagi
Jabatan HSKP juga semakin meningkat—

399
00:17:27,790 --> 00:17:29,390
jauh melebihi unjuran kami.

400
00:17:33,030 --> 00:17:34,720
Cukuplah berita gembira itu.

401
00:17:34,720 --> 00:17:36,000
Seterusnya, mari kita miliki

402
00:17:36,000 --> 00:17:37,110
Encik Xue

403
00:17:37,110 --> 00:17:37,830
taklimat kepada kami

404
00:17:37,830 --> 00:17:39,560
pada kerja resepsi esok.

405
00:17:48,550 --> 00:17:50,400
Bilangan kumpulan alumni esok

406
00:17:50,400 --> 00:17:51,310
lebih 100.

407
00:17:51,720 --> 00:17:52,380
Antaranya,

408
00:17:52,830 --> 00:17:54,720
terdapat 68 warga emas

409
00:17:54,720 --> 00:17:56,120
yang berumur lebih 80 tahun.

410
00:17:56,640 --> 00:17:58,110
Kita perlu menampung keperluan mereka

411
00:17:58,110 --> 00:17:59,430
sebanyak mungkin.

412
00:17:59,510 --> 00:18:00,240
Contohnya,

413
00:18:00,240 --> 00:18:01,880
pencahayaan dan pengudaraan

414
00:18:01,880 --> 00:18:02,940
dalam bilik tetamu,

415
00:18:03,110 --> 00:18:05,240
dan pilihan pemakanan tetamu.

416
00:18:05,440 --> 00:18:06,440
Jika perlu,

417
00:18:06,440 --> 00:18:08,570
kami boleh menyediakan beberapa perkhidmatan perubatan.

418
00:18:12,310 --> 00:18:12,960
Hello.

419
00:18:13,000 --> 00:18:14,130
Saya ingin mendaftar masuk.

420
00:18:16,400 --> 00:18:18,600
Anda mahukan bilik yang menghadap ke selatan, bukan?

421
00:18:18,640 --> 00:18:19,110
ya.

422
00:18:19,240 --> 00:18:20,370
Biar saya periksa untuk awak.

423
00:18:20,840 --> 00:18:23,690
[Pusat Status Bilik]

424
00:18:25,340 --> 00:18:29,110
[Bilik Eksekutif 1812]

425
00:18:28,790 --> 00:18:29,640
Dia...

426
00:18:30,190 --> 00:18:31,400
