472
00:21:11,790 --> 00:21:12,680
Encik Ji,

473
00:21:13,240 --> 00:21:15,040
apa yang saya baru laporkan kepada awak?

474
00:21:17,510 --> 00:21:20,000
Saya... saya tanya soalan yang salah.
Saya ingin bertanya tentang

475
00:21:20,000 --> 00:21:20,480
dewan jamuan.

476
00:21:20,480 --> 00:21:22,400
16 meja, 182 orang.

477
00:21:25,480 --> 00:21:26,480
By the way, Encik Ji.

478
00:21:27,240 --> 00:21:29,700
Berapa ramai alumni yang datang
untuk reunion lagi?

479
00:21:41,000 --> 00:21:41,750
Encik Ji,

480
00:21:42,790 --> 00:21:44,720
