482
00:21:46,720 --> 00:21:48,240
Saya berjaga lewat malam tadi

483
00:21:48,240 --> 00:21:49,550
dan tidak tidur lena.

484
00:21:49,550 --> 00:21:50,750
Otak saya agak perlahan.

485
00:21:51,270 --> 00:21:52,870
Anda hanya berdegil.

486
00:21:53,160 --> 00:21:54,270
Sebagai senior anda,

487
00:21:54,720 --> 00:21:56,920
izinkan saya memberi sedikit nasihat.

488
00:21:57,480 --> 00:21:59,240
Apabila hati anda mula bergelora,

489
00:21:59,240 --> 00:22:01,680
